Note This program defines a function that calculates the factorial of a number and prints the factorial of five.

Define a function called factorial that takes n.
  If n is less than or equal to 1, then.
    Give back 1.
  End if.
  Set result to the result of calling factorial with n minus 1.
  Set result to result times n.
  Give back result.
End function.

Set answer to the result of calling factorial with 5.
Display The factorial of 5 is answer.
